OL,3,CMan jailed for 'monstrous evil' attack
OL,4,Cthat has left baby profoundly disabled
OL,6,FA man who carried out "an attack of
OL,7,Fmonstrous evil" on a newborn baby and
OL,8,Fhas shown "no remorse" has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor more than 20 years.
OL,11,FTom Kember was found to have had a
OL,12,F"dangerous loss of control", and
OL,13,Fassaulted the baby in an "extreme,
OL,14,Fexplosive rage" leaving it with
OL,15,Flifelong disabilities.
