OL,3,CMan jailed for 'monstrous evil' attack
OL,4,Cthat has left baby profoundly disabled
OL,6,FThe assault happened at a property in
OL,7,FTaunton in January 2020, just 10 days
OL,8,Fafter the eight-week old baby had been
OL,9,Fdischarged from hospital, having been
OL,10,Fborn prematurely in 2019. The baby
OL,11,Fcannot be identified for legal reasons.
OL,13,FDuring Kember's trial, the 27-year-old
OL,14,Fdenied assault with intent to cause
OL,15,Fgrievous bodily harm but was found
OL,16,Fguilty by a jury on 30 October 2024.
OL,18,FA jury at Bristol Crown Court heard
OL,19,Fhow Kember did not initially dial 999
OL,20,Fafter the assault or take the baby to
OL,21,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
