OL,6,FThey were told that on 12 January
OL,7,F2020, Kember searched online for what
OL,8,Fhappend aif u (sic) hit a baby's face"
OL,9,Fand "can a baby be sick if it gets
OL,10,Fhit".
OL,12,FThey were also shown footage from
OL,13,Finside a McDonald's restaurant the
OL,14,Fnext day, where he and his partner,
OL,15,FKatherine Reilly, 25, were eating a
OL,16,Fmeal at about 10:45pm.
OL,18,FDuring this, he searched on his phone
OL,19,Ffor terms including "if baby hits its
OL,20,Fhead does the baby sleep a lot".
