OL,6,FThen, at about 1.20am on 14 January,
OL,7,Fthe couple called 111. It is estimated
OL,8,Fthat this was about 80 minutes after
OL,9,Fthe prosecution said a second assault
OL,10,Fhad happened, which caused brain
OL,11,Fdamage.
OL,13,FHe told the phone operator that the
OL,14,Finfant was unresponsive and an
OL,15,Fambulance was sent.
OL,17,FParamedics spotted bruising on the
OL,18,Fbaby's temples and raised their
OL,19,Fconcerns with staff at Musgrove Park
OL,20,FHospital on their arrival.
