OL,3,CMan jailed for 'monstrous evil' attack
OL,4,Cthat has left baby profoundly disabled
OL,6,FThe judge told Kember: "The victim of
OL,7,Fyour crime was extremely vulnerable at
OL,8,Fonly eight weeks old, after a
OL,9,Fpremature birth.
OL,11,F"The consequences where utterly
OL,12,Fcatastrophic, traumatic brain injury.
OL,13,FYou have robbed a child of most
OL,14,Fquality of life.
OL,16,F"This was an attack of monstrous evil
OL,17,Fwith the worst possible consequences."
