OL,3,CMan jailed for 'monstrous evil' attack
OL,4,Cthat has left baby profoundly disabled
OL,6,FHe added: "You show no remorse. This
OL,7,Fwas an extreme explosive rage,
OL,8,Fexerting forces far beyond rough
OL,9,Fhandling and similar to the force of a
OL,10,Fcar crash, or a fall from a height."
OL,12,FThe judge said Kember had two previous
OL,13,Fconvictions, one for domestic violence
OL,14,Fagainst a former partner and one
OL,15,Frelating to an incident with police
OL,16,Ffollowing his arrest in relation to
OL,17,Fthe baby's injuries.
