OL,6,FReilly received a six-month prison
OL,7,Fsentence, suspended for two years.
OL,9,FSentencing her, the Judge Lambert said
OL,10,Fthere was believed to be an 80-minute
OL,11,Fperiod between Kember inflicting the
OL,12,Finjuries and contacting 111.
OL,14,FHe told Reilly her actions in not
OL,15,Fseeking medical attention during that
OL,16,Ftime were "wicked and spineless", with
OL,17,Fmedical evidence stating that any
OL,18,Fdelay could have increased the harm to
OL,19,Fthe baby.
