OL,6,F"You betrayed the helpless injured
OL,7,Fbaby by shielding the wicked monster
OL,8,Fwho had so grievously injured them,"
OL,9,Fthe judge said.
OL,11,F"You seem to have no conscience and
OL,12,Fshow no regret for failing the child.
OL,13,FThe law is such that I cannot punish
OL,14,Fyou for your cowardly failure to
OL,15,Freveal the truth. Many decent folk
OL,16,Fwill think I should be able to do so."
