OL,6,FIn a statement, the child's adoptive
OL,7,Fparents described the impact of
OL,8,FKember's actions on their lives.
OL,10,FThey said: "There is not one part of
OL,11,Ftheir body that has not been affected
OL,12,Fby the injuries they sustained. They
OL,13,Fare in pain day and night."
OL,15,FThey described themselves as "angry
OL,16,Fand heartbroken" on behalf of their
OL,17,Fchild, whose future had been "stolen"
OL,18,Fby Kember.
